title: GTV IV GTA 4 Complete Soundtrack Radio
description:
The complete GTA IV soundtrack, including the songs for every station, and the jingles and links for the majority of the stations.

- Electro Choc: The complete mix ripped from the radio, and the songs separate
- Fusion FM: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- IF99 - International Funk: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- Integrity 2.0: All jingles, and four episodes
- JNR - Jazz Nation Radio 108.5: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- K109 The Studio: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- LCHC - Liberty City Hardcore: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- Liberty Rock Radio 97.8: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- Massive B 96.9: The complete mix ripped from the radio, with the songs separate
- PLR - Public Liberty Radio: All the jingles and three episodes
- Radio Broker: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- San Juan Sounds: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- The Beat 102.7: The complete mix ripped from the radio, with the songs separate
- The Classics 104.1: The complete mix ripped from the radio, with the songs separate
- The Journey: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- The Vibe 98.8: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- Tuff Gong Radio: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate
- Vladivostok FM: All the jingles and links, with the songs separate

All music files are labelled with ID3 tags, which have been checked for spelling, punctuation, grammar and accuracy

All music files have album art related to their radio station

Bonus: Niko Bellic's shouts.
